           <h2><a href="/resource/afc1993001.afc1993001_195995_03/?sp=4&amp;r=-0.546,-0.026,2.092,0.745,0"><span>Arabic class at St. Elias Maronite Catholic Church in Birmingham, Alabama, taught by Khattar Wehby, around 1915. Source: American Folklife Center, Ethnic Heritage and Language Schools in America Project collection
</span></a></h2>
           </div>
           </div>
       </li>
       
       <li 
           id="featured_public_domain_4">
           <figure>
               <a href="/resource/afc1993001.afc1993001_195995_03/?sp=19&amp;st=image&amp;r=-0.214,0.345,0.429,0.15,0" tabindex="-1">
